data.description: Beautiful 3-bed, 1-bath Ranch home on a huge corner lot with mature trees and alley access. Upon entry, there is a large Living Room with tons of natural light from the enormous front window. The spacious eat-in Kitchen features upgraded cabinets with dovetail drawers, tile backsplash, and a black composite sink. There are 3 spacious bedrooms all with gorgeous hardwood floors and a full bath with tile flooring. The laundry room is located just off of the kitchen and has direct access to the garage and the backyard. The large yard with a privacy fence has a concrete patio for outdoor entertaining and fun. There is a large side yard with plenty of room for your furry friends to roam. The home is near parks, schools, and shopping. Widefield Parks & Recreation has a new facility that is just minutes from the home that includes a gym, pool, library, and more. There are plenty of community events and activities. Don't miss out on this fantastic home in a warm & friendly neighborhood!
